investigations but most of all can represent a viable geometry to contrast to\nthe Kerr one in future phenomenological tests.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 18:22:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jul 2022 16:27:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 Dec 2022 17:01:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-05"}
