(2,\\mathbb{Z}_5)$ and singular along a degenerate\nabelian surface with $(1,5)$-polarization and level-$5$-structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2022 19:23:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2022 14:58:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-15"}
