cal beam performance is compared with\nmeasured RF patterns from both a fixed-point FFT as well as the proposed\nmultiplier-free algorithm and are in good agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 03:58:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
