y in signal is best probed by the\nsmall $k$-triangles in the squeezed limit and by triangles of similar shapes.\nThis opens up the possibility of constraining the source parameters during the\nCD using the 21-cm bispectrum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 09:01:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2022 14:24:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-16"}
