es. The upper estimates of the\nintegrated flux density of the detected RRATs are in the range 2-4 mJy at the\nfrequency 111 MHz.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 11:12:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
