rate that ANTI-CARLA can effectively and\nautomatically find a range of failure cases despite LBC reaching an accuracy of\n100% in the CARLA benchmark.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 01:05:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-15"}
